OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and widely sunny day
OL,6,Ftoday across the country, with perhaps
OL,7,Fsome cloud bubbling up later in the
OL,8,Fday. Another hot day with temperatures
OL,9,Fway above average for the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine and warm evening for
OL,12,Fmany, although the odd thunderstorm
OL,13,Fmay develop across the south.
OL,14,FRemaining warm overnight with plenty
OL,15,Fof clear skies.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAnother dry and sunny day,
OL,18,Falthough there is a small chance of
OL,19,Fthe odd shower developing in the
OL,20,Fsouth. Not as hot but still feeling
OL,21,Fvery warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
